 with your lovely pets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/5f12bdf380a31111ff595adbda0125d6.poster.avif?t=1725536750\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/5f12bdf380a31111ff595adbda0125d6.webm?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/5f12bdf380a31111ff595adbda0125d6.mp4?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Mining</strong><br>There are many minerals for you to find.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/7cf75cb924a09e523013eb1e5cf7dd56.poster.avif?t=1725536750\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/7cf75cb924a09e523013eb1e5cf7dd56.webm?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/7cf75cb924a09e523013eb1e5cf7dd56.mp4?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Diving</strong><br>Snorkeling to see beautiful coral reefs and have fun searching for items<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/7019c6277619e6bb834d6dbd64a74239.poster.avif?t=1725536750\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/7019c6277619e6bb834d6dbd64a74239.webm?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/7019c6277619e6bb834d6dbd64a74239.mp4?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore</strong><br>Set out to find small islands hidden in the sea. To meet new experiences<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/b9e9297102006003e726be0f5b421e51.poster.avif?t=1725536750\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/b9e9297102006003e726be0f5b421e51.webm?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036710/extras/b9e9297102006003e726be0f5b421e51.mp4?t=1725536750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Make friends</strong><br>Get to know the island people By giving gifts that he likes And sometimes you may get rewards or buy products at a cheaper price.",
